Description:
MAJESTIC MANNA ROW
"Overlooking a peaceful parkland and surrounded by native trees is a townhouse that feels anything but."
Almost like yin and yang, on the west side of the property you're greeted with modern living with all the benefits of the Arena estate, one of Officer's premier areas. On the east side you have a tranquil setting and your own private retreat where you'll be consumed by nature and a soft rising sun that greets you each morning.
All the while you are walking distance to the Cardinia Train Station, Arena shopping centre and some of the best local schools.
The townhouse itself is immaculate. Featuring:
- 3 bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- A well appointed kitchen with large stone bench tops;
- A dining area overlooking a separate lounge room;
- Another large living area upstairs;
- Heating and cooling;
- Private decked entertaining area;
- Double car garage with internal access.
Relax, unwind, welcome home.

ONE YOU CAN AFFORD
"Finally, here's your chance to enter the Officer market".
You've identified Officer as your preferred choice of purchase - and rightly so, it's an amazing town. The one problem was you could never afford the Officer price tag.
Well, guess what?! Now you can.
In the ever-appealing Arcadia Estate is the front unit of an appealing complex. Within walking distance to Cardinia Train Station, schools, shops and the appealing lake, the location is undeniably impressive.
The house, too, it quite unique.
Featuring:
- 2 bedrooms;
- Modern bathroom;
- Kitchen with open plan living and dining room;
- Ducted heating and split system cooling;
- High ceilings;
- Single car garage;
- Courtyard with low maintenance yard.

ONLY THE BEST TOLKIEN WILL DO
"When comparing authors, J.R.R. Tolkien is among the elite. When comparing properties 15 Tolkien Boulevard sets a similar standard."
Literally a few doors down the road is one of Arcadia's largest parks - complete with swing sets, walking trails and a basketball blacktop.
It's also walking distance to Bridgewood Primary School, Officer Secondary School and the Officer Specialist School. It's also supremely close to Officer train station plus the new retail complex currently being built off Siding Avenue.
Only two years old the property includes thousands of $$$ worth of upgrades.
Featuring:
- 4 bedrooms with spongy carpets;
- Master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- High ceilings - 2700mm to be exact and high-clearance doors of 2340mm;
- Kitchen with large upgraded stone benches and impressive see-through splash-back;
- Open plan living and dining room that includes upgraded floor boards and 3600mm stacker doors;
- Downlights throughout;
- Heating and cooling;
- European laundry;
- Double car garage;
- Low maintenance backyard.
